{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/A_Dark__Shifting_Mansion.png?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate a grand, decaying mansion where no two visits are ever the same. The ghost alters the layout, teleporting you to strange places and keeping you trapped in an ever-changing labyrinth.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/ADarkShiftingMansionGif.gif?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/Uncover_The_Past.png?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the mansion and uncover the tragic story behind the ghost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/UncoverThePastGif.gif?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/Eerie_Melody.png?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ghost\u2019s haunting melodies resonate through the mansion. Listen closely, as they may offer reassurance but may also foreshadow menace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/EerieMelodyGif.gif?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313430/extras/A_Haunting_Conclusion.png?t=1730246795\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you escape or confront the ghost, the ending is altered by your understanding of her tragic past.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap